  "description": "The Cot Chamber is a narrow sleeping room cut from Cindervale’s ancient ashlar and tightened with later blackened brick piers. A rope-lashed cot and a low plank chest occupy the long wall beneath soot-stained rafters, leaving a straight passage kept clear for quick compliance with quarantine ordinance. An iron-bound washstand and a lidded chamber pot emphasize the residence’s regulated domestic economy, while a small shuttered slit admits a hard bar of light from the survey-marker ring.",
